## Project Structure

```
power_grid_ai/
├── main.py                        # CLI entry point (rich terminal output)
├── server.py                      # FastAPI backend + SSE streaming
├── graph.py                       # LangGraph state machine + all agent nodes
├── requirements.txt
├── .env.example
│
├── tools/
│   ├── demand_supply_tools.py     # 6 tools: distance, supply chain, prices, capacity, weather
│   ├── health_tools.py            # 7 tools: runtime, sensors, health score, maintenance scheduler
│   ├── transmission_tools.py      # 7 tools: line data, loss calc, load balancing, flagging
│   └── orchestrator_tools.py      # 4 tools: system summary, conflict resolver, reward, next state
│
├── database/
│   └── db_setup.py                # SQLite schema + auto-seed (6 plants, 6 lines)
│
├── rl_env/
│   └── power_grid_env.py          # Gymnasium env wrapper with dynamic sensor perturbation
│
└── frontend/
    ├── src/
    │   ├── App.jsx                # Root layout + tab routing
    │   └── components/
    │       ├── CommandCenter.jsx  # Chat interface → /chat API
    │       ├── AutonomousRL.jsx   # Live RL stream → /stream SSE
    │       ├── PlantGrid.jsx      # Plant status cards → /plants API
    │       ├── GridMap.jsx        # Leaflet map of plant locations
    │       ├── StrategicIntel.jsx # Parsed report viewer
    │       ├── MemoryLog.jsx      # Decision + signal history
    │       └── Sidebar.jsx        # Navigation
    └── package.json
```

