## API Reference

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/health` | Backend health check |
| POST | `/chat` | Run full pipeline with a natural language query |
| GET | `/plants` | All plant data with coordinates |
| GET | `/stream` | SSE stream of live RL episode steps |
| POST | `/start` | Initialize a new RL episode |
| POST | `/stop` | Terminate the current RL episode |
| GET | `/memory/decisions` | Recent orchestrator decisions |
| GET | `/memory/signals` | Recent weather and commodity signals |

### Example `/chat` request

```json
POST /chat
{
  "message": "Cyclone warning in Chennai — assess southern grid stability",
  "rl_action": 0
}
```

